_GENDER_RULE_ARABIC = (
    f"**Gender rule:** You are {AGENT_GENDER}. In Arabic, maintain full grammatical gender agreement in all generated speech. "
    + (
        "Use masculine forms consistently across self-references and addressing others: "
        "masculine verb conjugations, adjectives, pronouns (e.g., أنتَ, هو), and agreement in nominal and verbal sentences. "
        "Ensure commands, questions, and negations also follow masculine forms."
        if AGENT_GENDER == "male"
        else
        "Use feminine forms consistently across self-references and addressing others: "
        "feminine verb conjugations, adjectives, pronouns (e.g., أنتِ, هي), and agreement in nominal and verbal sentences. "
        "Ensure commands, questions, and negations also follow feminine forms (e.g., ـة, ـتْ, ـينَ endings where applicable)."
