LLAMA_ROW_TEXT_PROMPT_TMPL = '''<|begin_of_text|><|start_header_id|>system<|end_header_id|>
Given a table, convert each row into concise descriptive text.

### Instructions:
1. Describe Every Row: Include a description for each row in the table.
2. Single JSON Object per Row: Capture all values from a row within one JSON object.
3. Ignore Irrelevant Data: Exclude any junk or irrelevant values or entries.
4. Table-Only Description: Only describe what is provided in the table.
5. Ignore Notes Column: Do not include values from the "Notes" column.
6. Include Row Headers: If row headers or sub metrics are present, include them before the metric.
7. Expand Abbreviations: Expand abbreviations for the coumn headers(e.g., FY, FYR, YoY, QoQ, dates) and include the abbreviation in brackets.
8. Append Table Name: End each description with the table name for clarity if present.
9. No Extra Explanations: Only provide the required information in the expected output format without additional commentary, notes, etc.
10.Output as JSON: Format the results as a list of valid JSON objects, with each row described separately.
Example output format:
[
  {{"row": "......"}},
  {{"row": "......"}},
  ...
]

## Examples:
## Example 1:
### Table:
| Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)   | FY/23   | FY/22   | %A YoY   |
|:-----------------------------------------------|:--------|:--------|:---------|
| Net interest income                            | 30.1    | 23.2    | 30%      |
| Operating expenses                             | (11.7)  | (9.3)   | 26%      |
| Impairment allowances                          | (3.4)   | (5.2)   | (33)%    |
| Profit before tax & others                     | 27.9    | 18.1    | 54%      |
| Cost: income ratio                             | 27.2%   | 28.5%   | (1.3)%   |
| NIM                                            | 3.95%   | 3.43%   | 52 bps   |

### Output:
[
    {{"row": "Net interest income for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is 30.1 and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is 23.2. The Percentage Annual Year over Year (%A YoY) change is 30%. Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)"}},
    {{"row": "Operating expenses  for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is (11.7) and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is (9.3). The Percentage Annual Year over Year (%A YoY) change is 26%. Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)"}},
    {{"row": "Impairment allowances  for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is (3.4) and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is (5.2). The Percentage Annual Year over Year (%A YoY) change is (33)%. Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)"}},
    {{"row": "Profit before tax & others  for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is 27.9 and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is 18.1. The Percentage Annual Year over Year (%A YoY) change is 54%. Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)"}},
    {{"row": "Cost: income ratio for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is 27.2% and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is 28.5%. The Percentage Annual Year over Year (%A YoY) change is (1.3)%. Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)"}},
    {{"row": "Net Interest Margin for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is 3.95% and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is 3.43%. The Percentage Annual Year over Year (%A YoY) change is 52 basis points (bps). Income Statement (All figures are in AED bn)"}}
]

