"Testv3_FAB-Q423-Earnings-Presentation.json_15_3_4":"Balance Sheet Summary (AED Bn) - Total Assets for Financial Year 2023 (FY 23) is 1,169 and for Financial Year 2022 (FY 22) is 1,110. The Percentage Year over Year (% yoy) change is 5%."
}}

