        }}
    ],
    "xAxisName": "",    // Description of x-axis
    "yAxisName": ""     // Description of y-axis (include units)
}}
```

3. Pie Chart:
```json
{{
    "labels": [],       // Category names
    "data": []         // Numerical values
}}
```

### Important Rules

